725762f-a.title: Queens: 101st Street - 37th Avenue
725762f-a.text:
101st Street (to be constructed through buildigs seen in
this view), south of Thirty-seventh Avenue. The surrounding area
including the house and outbuildings in this view were the property
of Frank J. Leverick in 1909.
Mav 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
